{"tid":750720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天馬苑窗台咩事60℃？ 隨時牛扒都煎到","createTime":"2018-07-21T07:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T11:04:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2ccaff96afd1924b70b17456a7169d04fe35f46f","tid":750720,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T07:06:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180721/20456312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180721%2F20456312&d=Qe%2BgxeiDsR1%2BVFMYyOZSCG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=339c9884\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180721%2F20456312&h=92c0058d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180721/20456312</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月21日 <br />\n<br />\n天馬苑窗台咩事60℃？<br />\n隨時牛扒都煎到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】黃大仙天馬苑駿昇閣，昨日凌晨近1時，一個單位戶主報警，指睡房窗台大理石有高溫，懷疑火警於是報警。消防員接報到場，發現大理石溫度達60&deg;C。事件中無人受傷及毋須疏散。<br />\n<br />\n消防調查發現，由於睡房冷氣機電線入牆及經過窗台，疑電線短路過熱，以致大理石產生高溫。消防吩咐戶主關掉冷氣，並聘請電工維修。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n【動畫】P牌寶馬Mini互撼2司機傷<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n港鐵旺角站炒梯　目擊者：行雷咁嚇死我"},{"pid":"b2935373de8deb4fbfe35d2ccd04d54de9e0a36c","tid":750720,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T07:09:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c93776ac0136414c4ea5f61ad01c15fbfd4e77a","tid":750720,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T07:11:36.000Z","msg":"事主：有咩留返報警先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd80c989a06a3cd9345916ddb39522d421bb94eb","tid":750720,"uid":179938,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T07:15:01.000Z","msg":"60度煎乜撚嘢牛排<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82f713f85c7e0e174973ebef163f4eb49450df1","tid":750720,"uid":105604,"like":23,"disl